title: BP.BP.road_centerline
name: BP.BP.road_centerline
description: The road centerlines for the Marine Corps Mountain Warfare Training Center, CA.  The data layers display the center of a roadway as measured from the edge of the driving surface.  Centerlines include paved and unpaved roads.  Road centerlines were digitized from 1998 and 1993 NAPP DOQs flown at a scale of 1:40,000 with a pixel resolution of 1 meter.
